Developer Terms of Use
des:
Stella Mac as the Director of Cosmic Cowgirls and Co-Director of the Color of Woman Teacher Training for the past 15 years has taught and witnessed the transformation of hundreds of women. The Wild Women Wisdom podcast is dedicated to sharing conversations with wild, wise women who are irreverent, reverent, and wildly, madly, uniquely themselves. You’ll hear from artists, teachers, authors, thought leaders, entrepreneurs, and rebels with a cause. Every conversation will inspire, awaken, and guide you in becoming your most fabulous, intentional, creative self.

Here are a few quick tips when navigating our skill. The First thing to note, when opening the skill you’ll be playing the latest episode, but if that’s not what you’re looking for, you can always find something more specific. This skill allows you to play next or previous episode. In addition, you can ask the skill to play the newest or oldest episodes or if you want to get specific, play a specific episode by saying the episode number. Try some of these commands:

**Next/Previous Episode**
— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, next”
— [While Episode Is Playing] = “Alexa, previous”

**Select Latest Episode**
— “Alexa, ask Wild Women Wisdom to play latest episode” 

**Select First Episode**
— “Alexa, ask Wild Women Wisdom to start from first episode”
